import { Box, Typography, Link, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import InstagramIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Instagram';
import WhatsAppIcon from '@mui/icons-material/WhatsApp';
import { useTheme } from '@mui/material/styles';

const Footer = () => {
  const theme = useTheme();
  return (
    <Box
      component="footer"
      sx={{
        background: theme.palette.background.default,
        color: theme.palette.text.primary,
        py: 4,
        px: 2,
        mt: 8,
        textAlign: 'center',
      }}
    >
      <Typography variant="subtitle1" sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
        Psicólogo Cristian Hendler  |  CRP 07/42111
      </Typography>
      <Box sx={{ mt: 1, mb: 2 }}>
        <Link href="#home" color={theme.palette.text.secondary} underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Início</Link>
        <Link href="#about" color={theme.palette.text.secondary} underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Sobre</Link>
        <Link href="#services" color={theme.palette.text.secondary} underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Serviços</Link>
        <Link href="#contact" color={theme.palette.text.secondary} underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Contato</Link>
      </Box>
      <Box sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: theme.palette.text.secondary, opacity: 0.85, fontWeight: 500 }}>
          by Vanessa Rocha
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
        <IconButton
          href="https://www.instagram.com/psicocrishendler/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main, mx: 1, '&:hover': { color: theme.palette.primary.dark } }}
          aria-label="Instagram"
        >
          <InstagramIcon />
        </IconButton>
        <IconButton
          href="https://wa.me/5551996024420"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main, mx: 1, '&:hover': { color: theme.palette.primary.dark } }}
          aria-label="WhatsApp"
        >
          <WhatsAppIcon />
        </IconButton>
      </Box>
      <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: theme.palette.text.secondary, opacity: 0.8 }}>
        © 2025 Cristian Hendler. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </Typography>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Footer;
